### Stats

* As of R version 4.0.0 of R released in April 2020 the default for `stringsAsFactors` was changed to false: (https://cran.r-project.org/doc/manuals/r-devel/NEWS.html)
* In the Data exploration chapter, link to explanations of distributions that appears in GLM chapter. 
* t & F tests: Explain that the default of na.action in t.test is to omit - you can check that by using getOption("na.action").  Have a look at https://www.rdocumentation.org/packages/stats/versions/3.6.2/topics/t.test 
